672
00:28:18,380 --> 00:28:19,260
Ignore him.

673
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:20,100
Let's go.

674
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:25,660
You two.

675
00:28:30,620 --> 00:28:31,460
Help me out.

676
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:53,420
What are you three doing?

677
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:54,860
Sitting so upright, like in class.

678
