A special episode?

683
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:08,580
I'm not interested.

684
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:13,580
Xinran.

685
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:15,340
Don't reject it so quickly.

686
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:16,260
Last time the show

687
00:29:16,260 --> 00:29:17,460
