Wen Cheng's been hosting for so long,

693
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,740
I've never seen anyone discuss him.

694
00:29:30,620 --> 00:29:33,420
The main person's chill,
but everyone else is losing it.

695
00:29:35,420 --> 00:29:36,260
Wen Cheng.

696
00:29:36,820 --> 00:29:38,060
Why do you always make us

697
