698
00:29:39,900 --> 00:29:40,740
Take the initiative.

699
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:42,940
I'll step aside with Yao Yuan for now.

700
00:29:43,260 --> 00:29:44,100
You two talk alone.

701
00:29:51,630 --> 00:29:52,940
What exactly do you want me to do?

702
00:29:53,310 --> 00:29:54,180
Kneel down

703
00:29:54,180 --> 00:29:55,060
