704
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:19,780
I'm going back to my room now.

705
00:30:19,780 --> 00:30:21,220
Wait, wait, don't go.

706
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:30,500
Let's go watch a movie.

707
00:30:31,740 --> 00:30:32,580
Okay.

708
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:33,620
Let's go.

709
00:30:37,420 --> 00:30:39,060
Yao Xinran, please.

710
00:30:39,060 --> 00:30:40,470
Just come on my show.

711
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:45,420
Wen Cheng.

712
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:47,260
Look at you.

713
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:49,900
If you're gonna kneel,
do it properly with both knees.

714
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:51,180
One knee down without a ring?

715
00:30:51,180 --> 00:30:52,180
No wonder Xinran got upset.

716
00:30:53,340 --> 00:30:54,300
