718
00:30:58,420 --> 00:30:59,260
Yuan.

719
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:00,900
Why is your face blushing?

720
00:31:02,420 --> 00:31:03,460
Is it?

721
00:31:04,340 --> 00:31:05,300
It's just stuffy in here.

722
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:06,830
I'm going to get some fresh air.

723
00:31:07,290 --> 00:31:08,140
See you.

724
00:31:08,140 --> 00:31:09,180
Sort out your own issues.

725
00:31:10,300 --> 00:31:11,140
Hey.

