732
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:33,580
Do I have to carry you into the studio

733
00:31:33,580 --> 00:31:34,500
so you can agree?

734
00:31:37,940 --> 00:31:38,780
Okay.

735
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:41,780
That's it?

736
00:31:43,220 --> 00:31:47,140
You don't want double pay,
but you want me to carry you?

737
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:50,450
Let me think about it again.

738
00:32:01,060 --> 00:32:02,340
Why is the power out?

739
00:32:14,300 --> 00:32:15,700
Sorry, I'll get the door.

740
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:21,180
Wow, you've had way too much to drink!

741
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,020
I miss you.

742
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:25,300
I've always regretted it.

743
