If it wasn't for my career,

744
00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:30,780
I wouldn't have been with Nana.

745
00:32:31,980 --> 00:32:33,060
When I saw you that day,

746
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:35,900
I decided I didn't
want any regrets in life.

747
00:32:37,980 --> 00:32:39,300
It's already over between us.

748
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:42,100
It's over, do you hear her?

749
00:32:43,860 --> 00:32:46,260
Mr. Zhuang, Xinran has made it clear.

750
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:47,660
The two of you are done.

751
00:32:47,860 --> 00:32:49,300
And she has a boyfriend now.

752
00:32:49,900 --> 00:32:50,740
It's me.

753
00:32:51,250 --> 00:32:52,190
Boyfriend.

754
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:53,300
- Sorry to bother.
- Bye, bye.

755
00:32:53,300 --> 00:32:54,420
Okay.

756
00:32:54,420 --> 00:32:55,300
Goodbye.

757
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:57,380
Going home.

758
00:32:58,300 --> 00:32:59,580
Alright, don't come back.

759
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:00,780
Bye.

760
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:04,700
He's drunk. It's not safe
for him to walk alone.

761
00:33:05,730 --> 00:33:07,290
