764
00:33:30,820 --> 00:33:32,340
I'm waiting for Yao Xinran.

765
00:33:35,850 --> 00:33:36,930
Where did she go?

766
00:33:37,020 --> 00:33:38,220
Why did she leave you here alone?

767
00:33:39,460 --> 00:33:41,070
