768
00:33:41,340 --> 00:33:42,180
How long has it been?

769
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:44,640
Does he live at the ends
of the earth or something?

770
00:33:46,220 --> 00:33:47,060
Zhuang Wei came?

771
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:51,010
Not just here,
