772
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,100
No.

773
00:33:56,980 --> 00:33:58,330
Why should I just wait around?

774
00:33:59,210 --> 00:34:00,060
That woman might have

775
00:34:00,060 --> 00:34:01,320
