really serious this time.

782
00:34:20,660 --> 00:34:21,580
I support him.

783
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:24,820
But why is Xinran taking so long?

784
00:34:37,740 --> 00:34:38,940
Xinran, you're back.

785
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:42,100
Are you okay?

786
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:44,670
