797
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:10,820
Don't go back to it again.

798
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:13,380
What about Wen Cheng?

799
00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:14,290
What will he do?

800
00:35:16,580 --> 00:35:17,820
What do you mean?

801
00:35:19,020 --> 00:35:20,460
He waited here for you all night.

802
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:22,460
He asked me to tell you

803
00:35:22,740 --> 00:35:24,860
