for a girl like this before.

804
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:26,740
He waited for me?

805
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:27,900
Hmm.

806
00:35:28,740 --> 00:35:31,010
I can tell he really likes you.

807
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:34,290
