your ex-boyfriend home.

808
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:35,950
How does that make him feel?

809
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:38,550
He even said he likes me?

810
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:39,740
He didn't say that.

811
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:40,940
I said it.

812
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:43,800
Why don't you ask him
what he's thinking?

813
00:35:44,180 --> 00:35:45,380
Probably nothing good.

814
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:53,100
Anlan,

815
00:35:53,340 --> 00:35:55,300
I did a really thorough
market research this time.

816
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:57,740
I interviewed everyone,
men, women, old, young.

817
00:35:58,060 --> 00:35:59,500
I even tried every cosmetic product

818
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:00,460
on the market,

819
00:36:00,460 --> 00:36:01,660
and analyzed their pros and cons.

820
00:36:04,100 --> 00:36:06,340
It took me three days
and nights to finish this.

821
00:36:07,660 --> 00:36:08,500
Not bad.

822
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:09,740
Given your abilities,

823
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:11,820
