824
00:36:13,780 --> 00:36:14,620
Anlan,

825
00:36:15,300 --> 00:36:17,300
don't I deserve some kind of reward?

826
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,300
At least treat me to a meal.

827
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:24,220
As an employee,

828
00:36:24,220 --> 00:36:25,740
completing tasks assigned by your boss

829
00:36:25,740 --> 00:36:26,700
is just part of the job.

830
00:36:34,180 --> 00:36:35,020
Anlan,

831
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:36,780
