832
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,220
What should I do next?

833
00:36:39,140 --> 00:36:41,580
Li Ao will explain it to you.

834
00:36:43,860 --> 00:36:45,380
Anlan, hey.

835
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:46,860
The rest of the work is teaching us

836
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,300
to know ourselves and the enemy.

837
00:36:48,820 --> 00:36:50,300
Since you've already done the analysis,

838
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:51,300
what you need to do next

839
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:52,780
is turn weaknesses into strengths.

840
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:54,780
Make them our bargaining
chips in negotiations.

841
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:58,540
