844
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:03,300
This time, you give it a try.

845
00:37:03,300 --> 00:37:04,140
See if you can nail it.

846
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:05,940
Alright, no problem.

847
00:37:06,620 --> 00:37:07,940
Whether it's a tough client or a saint,

848
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:09,380
they won't escape my grasp.

849
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:11,100
Good, get to work.

850
00:37:18,700 --> 00:37:19,700
Hey, hey, hey!

851
00:37:20,700 --> 00:37:21,540
Where are you going?

852
00:37:21,860 --> 00:37:24,300
I'm going to meet Mr. Jiang
from Faith Enterprises.

853
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,220
You're going alone?

854
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:27,060
I can definitely handle it by myself.

855
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:28,700
This is a task Anlan gave me.

856
00:37:28,700 --> 00:37:29,710
I have to do it well.

857
00:37:30,210 --> 00:37:32,190
Even senior managers
